@seekinc @youngrealtist @bnice_thegreenmachine 
@itsalreadysold @iluv_darling and all the other awesome folks who helped put on donate their time and money to make this possible!

@iluv_darling & I had the pleasure of doing the financial literacy and entrepreneurship workshops and these kids are on it ! 

One of the kids told me that he met me the day before because of an finance event I did at his middle school literally yesterday and told me that he doesn’t share his dream because folks don’t believe in him but he wants to tell me. We had a moment I shared some encouragement and we hit a fist bump, these are the kinda moments worth way more than money and why I’ll never stop giving back. ❤️ I believe in that kid but the fact that he’s in a room and program where everyone believes in him is where the long lasting impact is had. 

Happy Saturday 😇

